    "### 10.1 Main Effects\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Depth of Cut (ap)\n",
    "- F = 6.67, p = 0.0044  \n",
    "\n",
    "Depth of cut has a statistically significant effect on surface roughness. This indicates that variations in cutting depth produce systematic changes in surface quality even after accounting for within-run variability.\n",
