    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Cutting Speed (vc)\n",
    "- F = 1.85, p = 0.176  \n",
    "\n",
    "Cutting speed is not statistically significant. Its effect on surface roughness is not distinguishable from experimental variability within the current design.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Feed Rate (f)\n",
    "- F = 47.22, p ≈ 1.53 × 10⁻⁹  \n",
    "\n",
    "Feed rate is the dominant factor in the model. The extremely strong statistical significance indicates a robust and highly consistent effect on surface roughness across all experimental conditions."
